        "content": "<p>For the next meetup I'm thinking Sunday, June 21st at 7pm. (I'm aware it's Father's Day.) At <a href=\"https://www.timeout.com/time-out-market-boston\">Time Out Market</a> in the Fenway (<a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/Rxc91vumkD2PRJmu8\">map</a>).</p>",
        "id": 599135248,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1780314184
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I can do the 14th but it's only two weeks away. Seems a bit too soon.</p>",
        "id": 599135371,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1780314221
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I can't do the 31st because I'll be out of town. If people really prefer that date, please feel free to meet without me!</p>",
        "id": 599135572,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1780314266
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I mean, we also went a long time between the previous meetup and the one before, so maybe a shorter gap to get back to ~ mid month meeting isnt a bad thing?</p>",
