    {
        "content": "<p>Let's ping some regulars like <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"655359\">@Dan</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"659178\">@Pete</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"712386\">@Yamil Suarez</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"815615\">@Dave Hanft</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"775680\">@Tanmay Sharma</span> to see if we can get another <span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> for Sunday, June 14th at 7pm.</p>",
