    {
        "content": "<p>I just <a href=\"https://github.com/bostonopen/bostonopen.github.io/commit/99d3c13a5ada986ae49d4946383c719e440ace16\">updated</a> the website to say we're meeting on June 21st. At Time Out. At 7pm. See you there! <a href=\"https://bostonopen.dev\">https://bostonopen.dev</a></p>",
