    {
        "content": "<p>I just sent an email invite (bcc, of course). If you didn't get it and want to, lemme know. I may not have your address. <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span></p>",
