        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"712386\">@Yamil Suarez</span> brought it to my attention that the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2026_FIFA_World_Cup_Group_H#Uruguay_vs_Cape_Verde\">Cape Verde vs. Uruguay game</a> is Sunday at 6pm. I might head over to Time Out a bit early to watch. Plus, it might be loud! <span aria-label=\"flag cape verde\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f1e8-1f1fb\" role=\"img\" title=\"flag cape verde\">:flag_cape_verde:</span> <span aria-label=\"soccer\" class=\"emoji emoji-26bd\" role=\"img\" title=\"soccer\">:soccer:</span> <span aria-label=\"flag uruguay\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f1fa-1f1fe\" role=\"img\" title=\"flag uruguay\">:flag_uruguay:</span></p>",
